# Summary
This documentation page describes the AppsFlyer (Cohort) destination integration that allows sending Amplitude cohorts to AppsFlyer Audiences for personalized marketing initiatives. It covers setup requirements including obtaining AppsFlyer App ID and API token, configuring the destination in Amplitude with proper user identifier mapping, and the step-by-step process for syncing cohorts.

